===Got time for a chat?===
{{Messages|text=
:'''Xueyi:''' Got time for a chat?
:{Choice} Sure thing. What about?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Sure thing. What do you wanna chat about, Madam Xueyi?
::'''Xueyi:''' You seem to be free, which is great
:{Choice} I thought you never chat
::'''(Trailblazer):''' I thought you were a woman of few words, as you usually seem quite taciturn
::'''Xueyi:''' I do get taciturn
::'''Xueyi:''' But I can talk just as normal
:'''Xueyi:''' Just finished a mission. Got a few perplexities, reckon I could inquire of thee?
:'''Xueyi:''' The Ten-Lords Commission was notified that someone had been flooding the internet with claims "I'm mara-struck"
:'''Xueyi:''' There were lots of posts like that
:'''Xueyi:''' It seemed to be a call for help
:'''Xueyi:''' So, I went and did some sleuthing
:{Choice} The mara-struck claim is real?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' The mara-struck claim isn't real, right?
::'''Xueyi:''' No
::'''Xueyi:''' He doesn't even have any early symptoms of it
:{Choice} Was it just some internet shenanigans?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' I reckon it was just some internet shenanigans, right?
::'''Xueyi:''' Seems like you have crossed paths with many who are full of hot air
::'''Xueyi:''' He isn't mara-struck, and he doesn't even have any early symptoms of it.
:'''Xueyi:''' I have some free time now after making sure he's not mara-struck.
:'''Xueyi:''' So, why does he go around and tell everyone he is mara-struck? I'm baffled.
:{Choice} He is using it as a get-out-of-jail-free card
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Perhaps, by claiming so, he can use it as a get-out-of-jail-free card
::'''(Trailblazer):''' "Don't mess with me, because I'm mara-struck." Something like that
::'''Xueyi:''' I see. Now I get it
::'''Xueyi:''' In other words, he doesn't want to be responsible for his words and actions
:{Choice} It could be just a playful remark
::'''(Trailblazer):''' It could be just a self-deprecating and playful remark. I've seen similar ones
::'''(Trailblazer):''' "I could have become mara-struck without you!" Something like that
::'''Xueyi:''' Do people think it's funny?
::'''Xueyi:''' Seems like I don't have a good sense of humor?
:'''Xueyi:''' To me, being mara-struck isn't something one should joke about
:'''Xueyi:''' Thank you. I've learned a lot from this conversation
