===(Trailblazer), I need your advice.===
{{Messages|text=
:'''Xueyi:''' (Trailblazer), I need your advice.
:{Choice} Advice?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Sure thing. What is it about, Madam Xueyi?
::'''Xueyi:''' Thank you.
:{Choice} Are you sure about that?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Are you sure about that? My advice might not be advisable. Do take it with many a grain of salt
::'''Xueyi:''' Good enough for me
:'''Xueyi:''' You know my sister, Hanya, don't you? She works in the netherworld and is always on duty
:'''Xueyi:''' I'd like to send her a gift
:'''Xueyi:''' I'm not good at choosing gifts, so I'd like to ask for your advice
:{Choice} Fancy clothing, beauty products etc.
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Madam Hanya is very pretty. I'm sure you won't go wrong with getting her some nice clothing or beauty products
::'''Xueyi:''' Yeah, she's pretty
::'''Xueyi:''' But I'm bad at choosing such gifts
:{Choice} Simple words of appreciation
::'''(Trailblazer):''' You don't always have to send physical stuff. Sometimes, just a simple "thank you" will do
::'''Xueyi:''' I've told her that many times before
::'''Xueyi:''' It's not enough
:{Choice} What does Hanya like?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' To send someone a gift, we need to know their preferences first. What does Madam Hanya like?
::'''Xueyi:''' She likes to write novels
::'''Xueyi:''' But she doesn't need any more stationery or books
:'''Xueyi:''' If there's nothing special with the gift, I bet she'll just take it and put it aside
:'''Xueyi:''' Is there a more suitable gift for someone like my sister?
:{Choice} Time
::'''(Trailblazer):''' This may sound a little abstract, but I think what Madam Hanya needs is time.
:{Choice} Company
::'''(Trailblazer):''' This may sound a little abstract, but I think what Madam Hanya needs is company
:'''(Trailblazer):''' You can go shopping or watch an immersia with her. Spending time with her is your gift to her
:'''Xueyi:''' I never thought of this...
:'''Xueyi:''' I'll ask her
:'''Xueyi:''' Thank you, (Trailblazer)
:'''Xueyi:''' Huohuo's right to say that I need advice from someone mortal
:'''Xueyi:''' Sorry, wrong words
:'''Xueyi:''' I meant to say someone who lives in the mortal world
:'''Xueyi:''' Until next time
